import styled from "styled-components"

const Container = styled.div`
  flex: 1;
  margin
`;

const Product = ({item}) => {
  return (
    <Container>
        <Circle/>
        <Image/>
        <Info>
            <Icon>
              <ShoppingCartOutlined/>
            </Icon>
            <Icon>
              <SearchOutlied/>
            </Icon>
            <Icon>
              <FavoriteBorderOutlined/>
            </Icon>
        </Info>
    </Container>
  )
}

export default Product
